The second hypothesis was addressed using a planned two-step process. In the first step, individual regressions, similar to what is done in N-of-1 or single-case designs, were estimated for each patient with time predicting RSA values, ignoring session, using the ddply and lm functions in R:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
